INFO  2022-03-27 11:00:20,461 [34   ] oft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command - Executed DbCommand (34ms) [Parameters=[@__input_ChannelId_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__input_Status_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_2='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_3='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [i].[Id], [i].[StockCode], [i].[Status], [i].[CapitalCost], [i].[MarketPrice], [i].[TotalAmountBuy], [i].[TotalAmountSell], [i].[TotalMoneyBuy], [i].[TotalMoneySell], [i].[Vol], CASE
    WHEN [i].[CapitalCost] > 0.0 THEN (([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * CAST(100 AS real)) / [i].[CapitalCost]
    ELSE CAST(0 AS real)
END AS [GainLossPercent], ([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * CAST([i].[Vol] AS real) AS [GainLossValue], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN [i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]
    ELSE CAST(0 AS real)
END AS [SellInterest], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN (([i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]) * CAST(100 AS real)) / [i].[TotalMoneySell]
    ELSE CAST(0 AS real)
END AS [SellInterestPercent]
FROM [Investments] AS [i]
WHERE ([i].[ChannelId] = @__input_ChannelId_0) AND ([i].[Status] = @__input_Status_1)
ORDER BY [i].[StockCode]
OFFSET @__p_2 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_3 ROWS ONLY

    ELSE CAST(0 AS real)

    WHEN [i].[CapitalCost] > 0.0 THEN (([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * CAST(100 AS real)) / [i].[CapitalCost]
    ELSE CAST(0 AS real)
END AS [GainLossPercent], ([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * CAST([i].[Vol] AS real) AS [GainLossValue], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN [i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]
    ELSE CAST(0 AS real)
END AS [SellInterest], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN (([i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]) * CAST(100 AS real)) / [i].[TotalMoneySell]
    ELSE CAST(0 AS real)
END AS [SellInterestPercent]
FROM [Investments] AS [i]

ORDER BY [i].[StockCode]

    WHEN [i].[CapitalCost] > 0.0 THEN (([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * CAST(100 AS real)) / [i].[CapitalCost]
    ELSE CAST(0 AS real)
END AS [GainLossPercent], ([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * CAST([i].[Vol] AS real) AS [GainLossValue], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN [i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]
    ELSE CAST(0 AS real)
END AS [SellInterest], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN (([i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]) * CAST(100 AS real)) / [i].[TotalMoneySell]

END AS [SellInterestPercent]

    WHEN [i].[CapitalCost] > 0.0 THEN (([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * CAST(100 AS real)) / [i].[CapitalCost]
    ELSE CAST(0 AS real)
END AS [GainLossPercent], ([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * CAST([i].[Vol] AS real) AS [GainLossValue], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN [i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]
    ELSE CAST(0 AS real)
END AS [SellInterest], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN (([i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]) * CAST(100 AS real)) / [i].[TotalMoneySell]
    ELSE CAST(0 AS real)
END AS [SellInterestPercent]

    WHEN [i].[CapitalCost] > 0.0 THEN (([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * 100.0) / [i].[CapitalCost]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [GainLossPercent], ([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * CAST([i].[Vol] AS decimal(18,2)) AS [GainLossValue], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN [i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [SellInterest], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN (([i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]) * 100.0) / [i].[TotalMoneySell]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [SellInterestPercent]

    WHEN [i].[CapitalCost] > 0.0 THEN (([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * 100.0) / [i].[CapitalCost]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [GainLossPercent], ([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * CAST([i].[Vol] AS decimal(18,2)) AS [GainLossValue], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN [i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [SellInterest], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN (([i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]) * 100.0) / [i].[TotalMoneySell]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [SellInterestPercent]

    WHEN [i].[CapitalCost] > 0.0 THEN (([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * 100.0) / [i].[CapitalCost]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [GainLossPercent], ([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * CAST([i].[Vol] AS decimal(18,2)) AS [GainLossValue], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN [i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [SellInterest], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN (([i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]) * 100.0) / [i].[TotalMoneySell]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [SellInterestPercent]

    WHEN [i].[CapitalCost] > 0.0 THEN (([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * 100.0) / [i].[CapitalCost]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [GainLossPercent], ([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * CAST([i].[Vol] AS decimal(18,2)) AS [GainLossValue], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN [i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [SellInterest], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN (([i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]) * 100.0) / [i].[TotalMoneySell]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [SellInterestPercent]

    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN [i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]
    ELSE 0.0

    ELSE 0.0

    ELSE 0.0
END AS [GainLossPercent], ([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * CAST([i].[Vol] AS decimal(18,2)) AS [GainLossValue], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN [i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]
    ELSE 0.0

    ELSE 0.0

    WHEN [i].[CapitalCost] > 0.0 THEN (([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * 100.0) / [i].[CapitalCost]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [GainLossPercent], ([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * CAST([i].[Vol] AS decimal(18,2)) AS [GainLossValue], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN [i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [SellInterest], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN (([i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]) * 100.0) / [i].[TotalMoneySell]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [SellInterestPercent]

    WHEN [i].[CapitalCost] > 0.0 THEN (([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * 100.0) / [i].[CapitalCost]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [GainLossPercent], ([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * CAST([i].[Vol] AS decimal(18,2)) AS [GainLossValue], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN [i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [SellInterest], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN (([i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]) * 100.0) / [i].[TotalMoneySell]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [SellInterestPercent]

    ELSE 0.0

    ELSE 0.0
END AS [GainLossPercent], ([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * CAST([i].[Vol] AS decimal(18,2)) AS [GainLossValue], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN [i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]

    ELSE 0.0

INFO  2022-03-27 14:39:41,062 [30   ] oft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command - Executed DbCommand (21ms) [Parameters=[@__input_ChannelId_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__input_Status_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_2='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_3='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [i].[Id], [i].[StockCode], [i].[Status], [i].[CapitalCost], [i].[MarketPrice], [i].[TotalAmountBuy], [i].[TotalAmountSell], [i].[TotalMoneyBuy], [i].[TotalMoneySell], [i].[Vol], CASE
    WHEN [i].[CapitalCost] > 0.0 THEN (([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * 100.0) / [i].[CapitalCost]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [GainLossPercent], ([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * CAST([i].[Vol] AS decimal(18,2)) AS [GainLossValue], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN [i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [SellInterest], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN (([i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]) * 100.0) / [i].[TotalMoneySell]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [SellInterestPercent]
FROM [Investments] AS [i]
WHERE ([i].[ChannelId] = @__input_ChannelId_0) AND ([i].[Status] = @__input_Status_1)

INFO  2022-03-27 14:51:00,556 [19   ] oft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command - Executed DbCommand (4ms) [Parameters=[@__input_ChannelId_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__input_Status_1='?' SELECT [i].[Id], [i].[StockCode], [i].[Status], [i].[CapitalCost], [i].[MarketPrice], [i].[TotalAmountBuy], [i].[TotalAmountSell], [i].[TotalMoneyBuy], [i].[TotalMoneySell], [i].[Vol], CASE
    WHEN [i].[CapitalCost] > 0.0 THEN (([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * 100.0) / [i].[CapitalCost]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [GainLossPercent], ([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * CAST([i].[Vol] AS decimal(18,2)) AS [GainLossValue], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN [i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [SellInterest], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN (([i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]) * 100.0) / [i].[TotalMoneySell]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [SellInterestPercent]
FROM [Investments] AS [i]
WHERE ([i].[ChannelId] = @__input_ChannelId_0) AND ([i].[Status] = @__input_Status_1)
ORDER BY [i].[StockCode]
OFFSET @__p_2 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_3 ROWS ONLY

SELECT [i].[Id], [i].[StockCode], [i].[Status], [i].[CapitalCost], [i].[MarketPrice], [i].[TotalAmountBuy], [i].[TotalAmountSell], [i].[TotalMoneyBuy], [i].[TotalMoneySell], [i].[Vol], CASE
    WHEN [i].[CapitalCost] > 0.0 THEN (([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * 100.0) / [i].[CapitalCost]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [GainLossPercent], ([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * CAST([i].[Vol] AS decimal(18,2)) AS [GainLossValue], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN [i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [SellInterest], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN (([i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]) * 100.0) / [i].[TotalMoneySell]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [SellInterestPercent]
FROM [Investments] AS [i]
WHERE ([i].[ChannelId] = @__input_ChannelId_0) AND ([i].[Status] = @__input_Status_1)
ORDER BY [i].[StockCode]
OFFSET @__p_2 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_3 ROWS ONLY

INFO  2022-03-27 15:04:55,309 [27   ] oft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command - Executed DbCommand (4ms) [Parameters=[@__input_ChannelId_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__input_Status_1='?' SELECT [i].[Id], [i].[StockCode], [i].[Status], [i].[CapitalCost], [i].[MarketPrice], [i].[TotalAmountBuy], [i].[TotalAmountSell], [i].[TotalMoneyBuy], [i].[TotalMoneySell], [i].[Vol], CASE
    WHEN [i].[CapitalCost] > 0.0 THEN (([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * 100.0) / [i].[CapitalCost]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [GainLossPercent], ([i].[MarketPrice] - [i].[CapitalCost]) * CAST([i].[Vol] AS decimal(18,2)) AS [GainLossValue], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN [i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [SellInterest], CASE
    WHEN [i].[Status] = 2 THEN (([i].[TotalMoneySell] - [i].[TotalMoneyBuy]) * 100.0) / [i].[TotalMoneySell]
    ELSE 0.0
END AS [SellInterestPercent]
FROM [Investments] AS [i]
WHERE ([i].[ChannelId] = @__input_ChannelId_0) AND ([i].[Status] = @__input_Status_1)
ORDER BY [i].[StockCode]
OFFSET @__p_2 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_3 ROWS ONLY
